{\f2\fs18 \line - useAudioPlayer.ts: Logs audio element creation, source URL, load events,\line   play/pause state changes, error events with error codes, and duration detection\line - TranscriptViewerPage.tsx: Logs media URL resolution, file type detection,\line   and player initialization\line - Server: Added media-type-aware response headers for audio streaming}
